OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FA month after the government banned
OL,7,Fdisposable vapes, ITV News has heard
OL,8,Ffrom consumers and experts who say the
OL,9,Fregulations may not go far enough in
OL,10,Ftackling what's been dubbed the
OL,11,F'vapocalypse'. ITV News Digital
OL,12,FReporter Sam Leader explains
OL,14,FOn the June 1, 2025, the UK's
OL,15,Fdisposable vape ban came into effect
OL,16,Fmaking it illegal to sell single-use
OL,17,Fvapes and allowing only devices that
OL,18,Fare both rechargeable and refillable
OL,19,Fon the market.
