OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FVapers are now able to buy similar
OL,7,Flooking devices to before, but now
OL,8,Fwith a new charging port and the
OL,9,Fability to change the liquid 'pods'
OL,10,Fwithin the vapes themselves.
OL,12,FIt was partly in an effort to cut
OL,13,Fwaste as disposable vapes are
OL,14,Fdescribed as one of the most
OL,15,Fenvironmentally damaging products ever
OL,16,Fmade, but a quick trip down the high
OL,17,Fstreet quickly leaves you with the
OL,18,Ffeeling that there's some fundamental
OL,19,Fflaws in the new regulation.
