OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FTo find out how accessible liquid pods
OL,7,Freally are, I walked a mile down a
OL,8,Fbusy street lined with corner shops,
OL,9,Ftiming how long it would take to find
OL,10,Fone in a convenience store.
OL,12,FSix stores later, I was yet to find a
OL,13,Frefill for any of the most popular
OL,14,Fvapes that are currently on the market.
OL,16,F"It's better for you to just buy a
OL,17,Fbrand new vape", one shopkeeper said,
OL,18,F"they're not cheaper they're the same".
OL,20,F"So it kind of makes the whole thing
OL,21,Fpointless?" I asked.
