OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FThrough the Environmental Protection
OL,7,FRegulations 2024, the government made
OL,8,Fit illegal for retailers to sell,
OL,9,Foffer to sell or have in their
OL,10,Fpossession for sale disposable vaping
OL,11,Fproducts in their shop or on their
OL,12,Fwebsite.
OL,14,FVapes on sale must therefore be
OL,15,Frefillable and rechargeable, and if a
OL,16,Fbusiness does not comply, a #200 fine
OL,17,Fcan be issued and trading standards
OL,18,Fcan prohibit a business from selling
OL,19,Fvape products.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
