OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FAll retailers selling products must
OL,7,Fnow also offer a recycling bin for
OL,8,Fvapes, in order to negate the
OL,9,Fenvironmental impact from discarding
OL,10,Fthe vapes with regular litter.
OL,12,FMany of the most popular vape
OL,13,Fproducers now offer customers similar
OL,14,Fproducts to before but with a new 'pod
OL,15,Fsystem' and rechargeable battery.
OL,17,FThe pod is essentially a container
OL,18,Fthat is separately available and can
OL,19,Fbe replaced by a user so the vape can
OL,20,Fcontinue its normal course of use.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
