OL,6,FBut under the new guidelines, stores
OL,7,Fare not explicitly mandated to stock
OL,8,Fthe separate pods and coils for the
OL,9,Fnew vape products.
OL,11,FIt's highlighted concerns among users
OL,12,Fand experts that if the pods are not
OL,13,Freadily available then rather than
OL,14,Fusing the updated vapes as reusable,
OL,15,Fvapers will continue to use them as
OL,16,Fdisposable.
