OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FResearch by Material Focus suggests
OL,7,F1.2 billion disposable style vapes
OL,8,Fhave been bought since 2022 and three
OL,9,Fquarters of a billion disposable style
OL,10,Fvapes have been binned or littered.
OL,12,FNiamh McBride, Local Authority and
OL,13,FEnvironmental Partnerships Manager at
OL,14,FMaterial Focus, told ITV News: "Our
OL,15,Fconcern is a lot of the new models
OL,16,Fcoming onto the market look very
OL,17,Fsimilar to the old single use
OL,18,Fproducts. They have a similar look,
OL,19,Fsimilar feel and price point, which is
OL,20,Freally confusing for consumers."
