OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FChris Noice, communications director
OL,7,Fwith the Association of Shopkeepers
OL,8,Fsaid: "One of the biggest frustrations
OL,9,Fretailers have had is that they are
OL,10,Fselling rechargeable and refillable
OL,11,Fvapes, but they're not able to get
OL,12,Fhold of the pods.
OL,14,F"It's not for a lack of trying.
OL,15,FRetailers are trying to get hold of
OL,16,Fthem... It's a real problem with the
OL,17,Fregulations at the moment... and
OL,18,Fsuppliers need to do more. They need
OL,19,Fto make these pods available on the
OL,20,Fmarket and get them into more
OL,21,Fretailers."
