OL,3,C'Vapocalypse': Is the disposable vape
OL,4,Cban a game changer or a total flop?
OL,6,FWhen it comes to recycling, Noice told
OL,7,FITV News that so far they have seen
OL,8,Fvery little difference in the rate
OL,9,Fpeople are dropping off their devices
OL,10,Fto be stripped for parts.
OL,12,F"Retailers typically tell us that
OL,13,Ftheir recycling bins fill up every one
OL,14,For two weeks. So far, that hasn't
OL,15,Freally changed. So we haven't seen a
OL,16,Fhuge increase in recycling rates yet
OL,17,Fand maybe that's because people
OL,18,Fhaven't necessarily changed their
OL,19,Fbehavior."
