OL,6,FITV News approached the Independent
OL,7,FBritish Vape Trade Association for
OL,8,Fcomment who said: 'Our members are
OL,9,Freporting that sales of replacement
OL,10,Fpods are out stripping sales of the
OL,11,Fdevices, in many cases by a factor of
OL,12,Fbetween 3 and 9.
OL,14,F"This therefore would indicate that
OL,15,Fconsumers are aware that the devices
OL,16,Fare reusable and replacement pods are
OL,17,Favailable. The uptake in reusable
OL,18,Fproducts may have taken some suppliers
OL,19,Fby surprise, which may mean some
OL,20,Ftemporary supply issues.
